cutenews-client (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add option to override global command when setting custom download
    command.
  * Display popup when an article has no enclosures.
  * Bug fixes.

 -- Stuart Howarth <showarth@marxoft.co.uk>  Fri, 13 Oct 2017 17:21:41 +0100

cutenews-client (1.2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add option to open links in a built-in browser.
  * Add option to set a custom download command.
  * Add option to fetch an article from a URL via UI or 'showArticle' DBus method.

 -- Stuart Howarth <showarth@marxoft.co.uk>  Fri, 06 Oct 2017 02:05:16 +0100

cutenews-client (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add support for retrieving full articles from links where plugin is
    available.
  * Add support for portrait mode.
  * Add option to use volume keys to switch between articles.
  * Add widget.

 -- Stuart Howarth <showarth@marxoft.co.uk>  Mon, 02 Oct 2017 01:05:34 +0100

